title: indie / rock / dance / pop / rap Music Videos nov 15
description:
I like to make music video mixes for my work. My shifts are about 5 and a half hours long. I edit out the talky bits and run them through a program that does a decent job volume leveling them. It's hipstery for sure, I don't have too many HUGE artists on here.

Throw it in your favorite media player and put it on shuffle. Good for parties too I guess? Some of these videos are pretty bizarre/disturbing, just fyi
